            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "The flowers are in bloom here, too... They're so pretty..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If this is the place Ms. Odelia told me about..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3e,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Welcome...is what I would like to say, but I cannot allow you to intrude any further."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3e,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Heed this warning, unbidden guest. Continue no further and leave the premises of my jurisdiction."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I knew it! So this is the cradle...<CR>In that case, I can't go back...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3e,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I am the one who protects the seed.<CR>I only exist to carry out my duty."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3e,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "As the one who protects the seed, I possess no desire to murder aimlessly. However..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3e,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If you proceed any further, I will presume you to be one who threatens the preservation of the seed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I came here to take Nio back. No matter what you say, I won't be going back without her!"
        }
    ]
